      <h2 class="w3-wide" style="font-size: 30px;">About Student Mentee</h2>
      <p class="w3-justify" style="margin-top: 70px; font-size: 18px;">Welcome to the Student Mentee Project at the Sathyabama Institute of Science and Technology. We are thrilled to have you join our dynamic and innovative community. Here, you'll embark on a journey of exploration, learning, and collaboration in the ever-evolving world of technology. Whether you're a seasoned professional or just beginning your IT adventure, you'll find endless opportunities to grow, excel, and make a meaningful impact.</p>
      <h2 class="w3-wide" style="font-size: 30px;">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="w3-justify" style="margin-top: 70px; font-size: 18px;">The Student Mentee Project is designed to connect students with experienced mentors who can provide guidance, support, and inspiration. Our mission is to foster a nurturing environment where students can develop their technical skills, enhance their academic knowledge, and build strong professional networks. We believe that mentorship is a powerful tool for personal and professional growth, and we are committed to helping our students achieve their full potential.</p>
